%F A258667 For n <= 5, a(n)=0; otherwise a(n) = Sum_{0<=k<=n-1}(-1)^k*(n-k-1)! Sum_{max(k-n+5, 0)<=j<=min(k,4)} binomial(8-j, j)*binomial(2*n-k+j-10, k-j).
